<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[I'm only 25% through the book. Something felt off, untrue, improbable about the book as I first began reading it. Then, surely, two things hit me: would a teacher send off a letter from a young boy asking a soldier if he kills people? Then, in regard to Luis: I'm pretty certain that off duty soldiers are not permitted to carry guns or weaponry while off base. Please correct me if I'm wrong.... Somebody. <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
