    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_1211337797" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1211337797" />
    <a title="Wendy" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1418580-wendy"><img alt="Wendy" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1231118403p2/1418580.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1211337797?book_show_action=true">Sep 16, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Wendy" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Wendy" href="/user/show/1418580-wendy">Wendy</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9781476738963" href="/book/show/18271235-we-are-called-to-rise">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1418580-wendy?shelf=sep-18">sep-18</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1418580-wendy?shelf=5000-books">5000-books</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1211337797" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6286810562687800136">A heartbreakingly wonderful debut novel! <br/>One of the most emotionally moving books I have read in a long time.<br/>This story is set in Las Vegas and is told by 4 unique and authentic characters; a Mom going through a divorce, an injured Army soldier, a CASA worker and a Albanian boy. Their lives intertwine in unusual ways when they finally come together in a single, shocking moment.<br/>Laura McBride loosely bases this novel on a real event. Her description of the landscape of Las Vegas outside the Strip </span>
  <span id="freeText6286810562687800136" style="display:none">A heartbreakingly wonderful debut novel! <br />One of the most emotionally moving books I have read in a long time.<br />This story is set in Las Vegas and is told by 4 unique and authentic characters; a Mom going through a divorce, an injured Army soldier, a CASA worker and a Albanian boy. Their lives intertwine in unusual ways when they finally come together in a single, shocking moment.<br />Laura McBride loosely bases this novel on a real event. Her description of the landscape of Las Vegas outside the Strip was remarkably in-depth. Her characters were wonderfully developed and believable.<br />A haunting, heart-wrenching and hopeful book!</span>
  <a data-text-id="6286810562687800136" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


