          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9781476738963" href="/book/show/18271235-we-are-called-to-rise">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7425446-julie?shelf=library">library</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7425446-julie?shelf=favorites">favorites</a>
