<div id="review_1069947916" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1069947916" />
    <a title="Elaine Mullane || At Home in Books" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/873807-elaine-mullane-at-home-in-books"><img alt="Elaine Mullane || At Home in Books" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1525361625p2/873807.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1069947916?book_show_action=true">Oct 02, 2014</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Elaine Mullane || At Home in Books" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Elaine Mullane || At Home in Books" href="/user/show/873807-elaine-mullane-at-home-in-books">Elaine Mullane || At Home in Books</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9781471132582" href="/book/show/22692900-we-are-called-to-rise">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/873807-elaine-mullane-at-home-in-books?shelf=readwomen">readwomen</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/873807-elaine-mullane-at-home-in-books?shelf=favourites">favourites</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1069947916" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15770650273285408677">I adored this book. It is a phenomenal debut by a very passionate and talented writer. Laura McBride is definitely one to watch.<br/><br/>I love how she brings out the beauty in the bad, and how she inspires us to look for that ray of hope in the sometimes devastating situations life can throw at us.<br/><br/>One of my favourite pieces of literary fiction in recent years.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


