 who aren\'t willing to make things right.\n\nWith deep empathy, therapeutic insight, and rich Bible teaching coming out of more than 1,000 hours of theological study, Lysa will help you:\n\n\nLearn how to move on when the other person refuses to change and never says they\'re sorry.\nWalk through a step-by-step process to free yourself from the hurt of your past and feel less offended today.\nDiscover what the Bible really says about forgiveness and the peace that comes from living it out right now.\nIdentify what\'s stealing trust and vulnerability from your relationships so you can believe there is still good ahead.\nDisempower the triggers hijacking your emotions by embracing the two necessary parts of forgiveness.<\/span>\n  <a data-text-id=\"737477690282397067\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"swapContent(\$(this));; return false;\">...more<\/a>\n\n    <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\'wtrButtonContainer wtrSignedOut\' id=\'24_book_52645353\'>\n<div class=\'wtrUp wtrLeft\'>\n<form action=\"/shelf/add_to_shelf\" accept-charset=\"UTF-8\" method=\"post\"><input name=\"utf8\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"&#x2713;\" /><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"authenticity_token\" value=\"OoDsLIGx+NttRT8yz3jyOiy7Xo0tdYwdyqTOrtZ0I3NNdi8mCOSXoA3/Qv9q4reymjBphvP+i86I3FvV1Jytrg==\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_id\" id=\"book_id\" value=\"52645353\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"name\" id=\"name\" value=\"to-read\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"unique_id\" id=\"unique_id\" value=\"24_book_52645353\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"wtr_new\" id=\"wtr_new\" value=\"true\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_choice\" id=\"from_choice\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_home_module\" id=\"from_home_module\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"ref\" id=\"ref\" value=\"\" class=\"wtrLeftUpRef\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"existing_review\" id=\"existing_review\" value=\"false\" class=\"wtrExisting\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_origin\