<span id="freeTextContainer17701580255901217651">Laura McBride is the author of In the Midnight Room (formerly &apos;Round Midnight), a 2017 Indie Next pick, and We Are Called to Rise, a #1 Indie Next pick in 2014. She&apos;s also a community college teacher. She takes her personal motto from the title of a book: make way for ducklings.<br/><br/><a target='_blank' rel='noopener nofollow' href='http://lauramcbrideauthor.com'>http://lauramcbrideauthor.com</a></span>
